title: New Zealand 2 Year Note Yield
description: New Zealand 2Y Bond Yield was 4.31 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the New Zealand 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 7.89 in August of 2007. This page includes a chart with historical data for New Zealand 2Y Bond Yield.
